{"tid":2189120,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎電影化橋段曝光，史詩程度堪比獨立日２","createTime":"2020-09-04T16:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T02:34:58.000Z","uid":8307,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b10320438b48e952c1bd00401d0a4900f439a17","tid":2189120,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:07:19.000Z","msg":"電影主要劇情講述係武漢肺炎爆發後，世界社會點樣係絕地中重生，拍攝手法同劇情內容比較似由庵野秀明所拍既真哥斯拉，已經確定會由知名導演執導。<br />\n<br />\n最近有小道消息流出劇情指<br />\n開頭第個shot影住地板，一路運鏡去到張枱上面，有人倒瀉蒙牛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/091644_1a70f47e34c3bf0740a0449126a239ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F091644_1a70f47e34c3bf0740a0449126a239ae.png&h=cbeb8cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信呢個scene就係病毒最初爆發既橋段黎<br />\n第二段流出劇情指有大量白人乘搭中國國際航空前往中國，機上面既乘客睇抖音既視頻以及騰迅既絕地球生消遣<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/zNBUwdTU4HE/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FzNBUwdTU4HE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=6f3e364a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鏡頭一轉，各國首腦代表用華為MatePad開zoom開會<br />\n<br />\n電影尾聲美國總統拿起華為手機，下個shot近鏡影住部手機畫面顯示出鴻蒙OS既LOGO，用普通話道出一句：「習總統求你幫幫我們。」<br />\n鏡頭一轉，影住老習個樣冷笑一下，鏡頭拉近<br />\n然後音樂奏起<br />\n燈等燈燈 燈等燈燈 燈等燈燈 燈等燈燈 燈燈 <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lelefarley/status/1292937094931705856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flelefarley%2Fstatus%2F1292937094931705856&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4wp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=ee30c10b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flelefarley%2Fstatus%2F1292937094931705856&h=06ffb454\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lelefarley/status/1292937094931705856</a>"},{"pid":"53eae65de7c85fc3d7d6fa46b969f59f6c290dd2","tid":2189120,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"dame dame dameyo"},{"pid":"37fd6ec4359e71802302b02442922757563f5d28","tid":2189120,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53eae65de7c85fc3d7d6fa46b969f59f6c290dd2","tid":2189120,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"dame dame dameyo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:08:53.000Z","msg":"dadadadadame"},{"pid":"2904843fea320151f31b30b511f54dd266b52a15","tid":2189120,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"庵野向記者表示：「相信是能超越EVA的新作。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3978219441d2d8d42aaeb3d641c6cccf5ca9ceb","tid":2189120,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53eae65de7c85fc3d7d6fa46b969f59f6c290dd2","tid":2189120,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"dame dame dameyo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"哥哇呢打 波咕爛嗲沙 依KI哦拖咩嗲"},{"pid":"9521f720b28d4024da158400d60fd3e595c50fb6","tid":2189120,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2904843fea320151f31b30b511f54dd266b52a15","tid":2189120,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"庵野向記者表示：「相信是能超越EVA的新作。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"超越唔到,因為拍完之後EVA既結局都仲未出"},{"pid":"fe4c809bfe9c497a6bea53e9754ecceddc336fb3","tid":2189120,"uid":31219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"此post含有0% ACG成份"},{"pid":"1660103ef08b867259f26bf0a9f27f7964421969","tid":2189120,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe4c809bfe9c497a6bea53